      <title>Mysql下载和安装</title>
      <link href="/posts/fb0e1638.html"/>
      <url>/posts/fb0e1638.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Mysql下载安装"><a href="#Mysql下载安装" class="headerlink" title="Mysql下载安装"></a>Mysql下载安装</h1><h2 id="第一步：下载"><a href="#第一步：下载" class="headerlink" title="第一步：下载"></a>第一步：下载</h2><p><a href="https://www.mysql.com/downloads/">MySQL :: MySQL Downloads官方网址</a></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/xz1.jpeg"></p><span id="more"></span><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/xz2.jpeg"></p><!-- more --><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/xz3.jpeg"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/xz4.jpeg"></p><h2 id="第二步：安装"><a href="#第二步：安装" class="headerlink" title="第二步：安装"></a>第二步：安装</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/az1.png"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/az2.png">    <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/az3.png"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/az5.png"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/az4.png">11.win+x打开Windows终端（管理员)，并输入以下指令</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysqld --initialize-insecure //初始化mysql，并生成root账户且不生成密码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysqld --install//安装</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>回车，如果出现以下提示代表安装成功<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/20200207193100951.jpg"></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">net start mysql //启动mysql的服务 net stop mysql停止mysql服务</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>回车，如果出现以下提示代表开启成功</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xubios/URL-image-file@main/images/2022/01/03/mysql/20200207194037108.jpg"></p><p>12.输入以下指令登入mysql</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql -u root -p //如果需要输入密码回车即可</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>13.依次输入以下指令来设置用户</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">use mysql;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">update user set user=&quot;自定义用户名&quot; where user=&quot;root&quot;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">flush privileges;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">alter user &#x27;上一步的用户名&#x27;@&#x27;localhost&#x27; identified with mysql_native_password by &#x27;密码&#x27;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>14.退出mysql</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\q</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此安装成功,谢谢观看</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
