      <title>Archlinux无法连接wifi</title>
      <link href="/posts/5f6cee1a.html"/>
      <url>/posts/5f6cee1a.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="问题："><a href="#问题：" class="headerlink" title="问题："></a>问题：</h2><p>1.archlinux安装过程中如何联网？？？</p><p>2.archlinux安装完成后进入图形化界面无法使用wifi只能使用网线</p><p>（manjaro Linux 可能适用）</p><p>下文是解决方法：</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="解决："><a href="#解决：" class="headerlink" title="解决："></a>解决：</h2><h3 id="archlinux安装过程中联网"><a href="#archlinux安装过程中联网" class="headerlink" title="archlinux安装过程中联网"></a>archlinux安装过程中联网</h3><p>指令依次往下执行，除注释外</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$dhcpcd#接入网线</span><br><span class="line">$iwctl#进入iwd模式</span><br><span class="line">$device list#列出网卡信息</span><br><span class="line">$station wlan0 scan</span><br><span class="line">$station wlan0 get-networks    #扫描并列出有用的网络</span><br><span class="line">$station wlan0 connect 网络名称  #连接网络</span><br><span class="line">$exit#退出模式</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="archlinux进入图形化界面后联网（wifi）"><a href="#archlinux进入图形化界面后联网（wifi）" class="headerlink" title="archlinux进入图形化界面后联网（wifi）"></a>archlinux进入图形化界面后联网（wifi）</h3><p>配置网络(指令依次往下执行，除注释外)</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">有线连接：</span><br><span class="line">$systemctl start dhcpcd#开启服务</span><br><span class="line">$systemctl enable dhcpcd#开机自启动</span><br><span class="line">#$systemctl stop dhcpcd 关闭服务</span><br><span class="line">无线连接：</span><br><span class="line">$systemctl start iwd#开启服务</span><br><span class="line">$systemctl enable iwd#开机自启动</span><br><span class="line">#$systemctl start iwd   关闭服务</span><br><span class="line">Linux使用图像化的网络管理器</span><br><span class="line">$pacman -S networkmanger#安装软件包</span><br><span class="line">$systemctl start NetworkManager.service #开启服务</span><br><span class="line">$systemctl enable NetworkManager.service    #开机自启动</span><br><span class="line">$pacman -S nm-connection-editor #安装图形化设置工具</span><br><span class="line">$pacman -S network-manager-applet</span><br><span class="line">$pacman -S xfce4-notifyd       #安装显示通知工具</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
